      • match

        public boolean match(int currentDay)
        Checks whether the object contains the day.
        E.g. ITime#DAY_MON_FRI contains 5 days from Monday to Friday.
        If the current day is Monday, the result is true. For Saturday the result is false because the object doesn't contain the day.
        Parameters:
        day - the current day
        Returns:
        true if the day exists otherwise false
